Welcome to uglyOS! 

The only default user is root!
You should add at least one user!
Your default passwd for root:	uglyostemppass

Commands to get you started (as root):
----------------------------
ugly-help				Interactive help
passwd					Change password
ugly-user-add <username>		Add a user
exit					Log out of a session
ugly-motd-kill				Kill this message for all users
ugly-issue-kill  			Kill the pre-login root pass hint
ugly-net-setup				Setup b43 wifi (requires network)
yast					Config stuff like wifi interfaces

Once you are logged in as a non-root user:
----------------------------
ugly-help				Interactive help
startx					Start a graphical session
su					Switch to root user
exit					Exit an su session (as any other)
ugly-motd-repeat			Repeat this message
